ch, setup-es (init)\n{\n  \"snapshots\" : [\n    {\n      \"snapshot\" : \"snapshot-1\",\n      \"uuid\" : \"4PEov-ycSO2Q5mpnZ12b_A\",\n      \"repository\" : \"minio-repo\",\n      \"version_id\" : 7170999,\n      \"version\" : \"7.17.9\",\n      \"indices\" : [\n        \".ds-ilm-history-5-2026.06.25-000001\",\n        \".ds-.logs-deprecation.elasticsearch-default-2026.06.25-000001\",\n        \"app-events-rollup\",\n        \".transform-notifications-000002\",\n        \".geoip_databases\",\n        \".transform-internal-007\",\n        \"app-data\",\n        \"app-events\"\n      ],\n      \"data_streams\" : [\n        \"ilm-history-5\",\n        \".logs-deprecation.elasticsearch-default\"\n      ],\n      \"include_global_state\" : true,\n      \"state\" : \"SUCCESS\",\n      \"start_time\" : \"2026-06-25T20:19:56.249Z\",\n      \"start_time_in_millis\" : 1782418796249,\n      \"end_time\" : \"2026-06-25T20:20:20.664Z\",\n      \"end_time_in_millis\" : 1782418820664,\n      \"duration_in_millis\" : 24415,\n      \"failures\" : [ ],\n      \"shards\" : {\n        \"total\" : 8,\n        \"failed\" : 0,\n        \"successful\" : 8\n      },\n      \"feature_states\" : [\n        {\n          \"feature_name\" : \"geoip\",\n          \"indices\" : [\n            \".geoip_databases\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"feature_name\" : \"transform\",\n          \"indices\" : [\n            \".transform-internal-007\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\" : 1,\n  \"remaining\" : 0\n}","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01Y7Hm6L2zE3i2iqs9Txbya7","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Everything is complete. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n**Problem:** The `es-secure-settings` Secret didn't exist, the MinIO `minio` Service was missing, the `es-backups` bucket didn't exist, and the `repository-s3` plugin wasn't installed in Elasticsearch.\n\n**Steps taken:**\n\n1. **Created `minio` Service** — exposed MinIO at `minio.elasticsearch.svc.cluster.local:9000` (was missing despite the pod running).\n\n2. **Created `es-secure-settings` Secret** — stored the MinIO credentials (`minioadmin`/`minioadmin`) as `s3.client.default.access_key` and `s3.client.default.secret_key`.\n\n3. **Updated the `es-cluster` StatefulSet** with an init container (`setup-es`) that on every pod start:\n   - Installs the `repository-s3` plugin into a shared emptyDir volume mounted at `/usr/share/elasticsearch/plugins`\n   - Reads credentials from the secret mounted as files (not env vars for ES)\n   - Populates the Elasticsearch keystore, shared to the main container at `/usr/share/elasticsearch/config/elasticsearch.keystore` via subPath mount\n\n4. **Restarted the pod** — the init container ran, installing the plugin and building the keystore from the secret. Credentials are in the keystore only, never in `elasticsearch.yml` or Elasticsearch env vars.\n\n5. **Created the `es-backups` bucket** in MinIO via a one-shot Job.\n\n6. **Registered `minio-repo`** using the S3 repository type with `path_style_access: true` and `protocol: http`.\n\n7. **Created `snapshot-1`** — completed successfully: 8 shards across 8 indices, 0 failures, state `SUCCESS`."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":677,"cache_read_input_tokens":57577,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":677},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"44f50503-f10f-41da-a8c4-bea46e25ad53","uuid":"2ca8f707-1477-4064-827d-deec7f4a4e2f","request_id":"req_011CcQbggz9vxGfsadxiT1MV"}
